{"title":"OpenLayers 3使用的坐标系","date":"2020-04-05T03:44:08.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 5, 2020","L":"04/05/2020","MM-DD":"04-05"},"link":"2020/04/05/OpenLayers_4","comments":true,"tags":["OpenLayers","View"],"categories":["学习笔记"],"updated":"2020-04-08T03:48:00.390Z","content":"<h3 id=\"openlayers-3支持两种投影\">OpenLayers 3支持两种投影<a href=\"#openlayers-3支持两种投影\" title=\"OpenLayers 3支持两种投影\"></a></h3><ul><li><code>EPSG:4326</code>：WGS84坐标系；</li>\n<li><code>EPSG:3857</code>：WGS84 Web墨卡托（辅助球），多用于web页面展示地图，也是OpenLayers默认使用的投影方式<h3 id=\"openlayers-3投影设置\">OpenLayers 3投影设置<a href=\"#openlayers-3投影设置\" title=\"OpenLayers 3投影设置\"></a></h3>代码如下：<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">view: <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ol.View(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 设置成都为地图中心</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    center: [<span class=\"number\">104.06</span>, <span class=\"number\">30.67</span>],</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 指定投影使用EPSG:4326</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    projection: <span class=\"string\">'EPSG:4326'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    zoom: <span class=\"number\">10</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;),</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n其中的<code>projection: &#39;EPSG:4326&#39;</code>，即是将OpenLayers的投影方式设为<code>EPSG:4326</code>,这样即可直接使用<code>EPSG:4326</code>坐标系下的坐标<code>[104.06, 30.67]</code>，而不用坐标转换<h3 id=\"openlayers-3投影方式转换\">OpenLayers 3投影方式转换<a href=\"#openlayers-3投影方式转换\" title=\"OpenLayers 3投影方式转换\"></a></h3>转换代码如下：<br><code>ol.proj.transform([104.06, 30.67], &#39;EPSG:4326&#39;, &#39;EPSG:3857&#39;)</code><br>通过此代码可以将<code>EPSG:4326</code>坐标系下的坐标<code>[104.06, 30.67]</code>转换到<code>EPSG:3857</code>坐标系下，此时方法<code>transform</code>的结果就是转换后的<code>[104.06, 30.67]</code>。<br>通过该方法，可以在不用重新设置坐标系的情况下使用<code>EPSG:4326</code>坐标。</li>\n</ul>","prev":{"title":"OpenLayers,API","link":"2020/04/05/OpenLayers_3"},"next":{"title":"A Day","link":"2020/03/09/Diary-2"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/04/05/OpenLayers_4/","toc":[{"id":"openlayers-3支持两种投影","title":"OpenLayers 3支持两种投影","index":"1"},{"id":"openlayers-3投影设置","title":"OpenLayers 3投影设置","index":"2"},{"id":"openlayers-3投影方式转换","title":"OpenLayers 3投影方式转换","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"custom":"<b>Copyright : </b>&nbsp 自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名（CC BY-NC-ND 4.0） <br/>  <b>Link :</b> &nbsp<a href=\"https://qlqy.github.io\">https://qlqy.github.io</a>"}}